262
00:21:07,770 --> 00:21:10,130
Này, Dong Goo.

263
00:21:10,130 --> 00:21:11,000
Suỵt.

264
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:11,870
Dong Goo.

265
00:21:11,870 --> 00:21:12,800
Suỵt.

266
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:14,640
Tôi đang đi nặng

