893
01:15:32,030 --> 01:15:33,330
Nhưng mà...

894
01:15:33,330 --> 01:15:34,560
Mau báo cảnh sát đi.

895
01:15:34,560 --> 01:15:35,770
Nhanh.

896
01:15:35,770 --> 01:15:38,000
Đi, đi mau.

897
01:16:02,390 --> 01:16:03,860
