01:16:11,370 --> 01:16:12,170
Bong Yi.

900
01:16:12,170 --> 01:16:13,240
Chú ơi, nhanh lên.

901
01:16:13,240 --> 01:16:16,070
Anh Ba Reum, anh Ba Reum, anh ấy...

